name: memrspn
short_description:
size_t memrspn (const void* buf, size_t buflen, const void* accset, size_t acclen);

memrspn() searchs the first buflen bytes of buf in reverse to find the first byte in buf that is not in the set of bytes that is in the first acclen bytes of accset.
